{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I haven't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I haven't because I was Horvath Laszlo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the-- in the-- in the cellar of this house by that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Being the only man in the house, looking after the women and, and, and the girls, I did the heavy work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was the hero there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- everybody-- you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To what extent, I tell you the last happening in that house, which was on the night of 18th of January.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now we are in January, right, of 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By that time, we realized that the Russians are very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We heard the, the loudspeakers in the vicinity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a house-to-house fighting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a horrible situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were in, in the-- in the-- in the-- in the cellar downstairs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Houses around us have been bombed to-- we couldn't recognize them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And food was getting less, right, for the non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were waiting for the-- for the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But even then, through misinformation and through, through wishful thinking, there was always, always hope in the-- in the non-Jewish population that a miracle will happen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Same what the Jews thought, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's in a human-- human trait.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and Merleg Street 33 was very close to the last bridge.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called the Lanchid, the [NON-ENGLISH], the, the Chain Bridge, which was the last link between Buda and Pest.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
